{"tid":2310601,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【玩命表演】試食元素周期表 螺獅粉包膠","createTime":"2020-12-03T11:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T13:51:45.000Z","uid":38539,"like":3,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e7e8614f2c268ae7bc4e8fd617546387b870200e","tid":2310601,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:21:09.000Z","msg":"前近日經過百佳，見到壽桃牌出咗隻即食螺獅粉，<br />\n價錢好平$11.x，份量好似幾足，於是買嚟試試，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XxJ31Xz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXxJ31Xz.png&h=c4713338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我係用微波壚個煮法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FjqBCvV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFjqBCvV.png&h=f1422df1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n配菜有花生、竹筍片、幾粒螺肉、木耳條<br />\n <br />\n優點﹕價錢好平$11.x，啲配菜幾足吓，螺肉都有兩舊，呢個價錢算係咁，味道幾好食，類似酸辣米線，小小辣。<br />\n<br />\n缺點﹕支叉勁撚細，拎嚟食野簡直係極難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">最大問題係碗野個氣味超臭，有陣超濃郁的豬大腸個陣超臭氣味，</span></span><br />\n我係間房仔食，連出面廳老豆老母都聞到好強烈刺鼻的臭味。<br />\n<br />\n結論﹕幾平幾好食，但唔會再買，因為個陣毒氣太搔擾到其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6684e5a67f8658690a40638210ca36bb5fe7a66","tid":2310601,"uid":153781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:27:57.000Z","msg":"有冇同螺獅粉隻抽？"},{"pid":"ddc94137ca76f01ccc9c5b1e2f5d387fc687f8f2","tid":2310601,"uid":144014,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:28:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXvudcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXvudcd.jpg&h=3e073d79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王同學，幾時食飯？"},{"pid":"f3f7fd55bd823761e4a41bc2d7ae0e39f2a10e78","tid":2310601,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddc94137ca76f01ccc9c5b1e2f5d387fc687f8f2","tid":2310601,"uid":144014,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11: